  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you cast a spell of 5th level or lower, you can spend a number of sorcery points equal to the spell's level to delay the spell, triggering it only when certain circumstances have been met. These circumstances are designated when you cast the spell and cannot be changed afterward. The conditions can be as simple or as complex as you like, but can only rely on your senses and knowledge. The spell's energy fades harmlessly after 8 hours if it has not been triggered.</p>",
